v1.0 aplpha
===========
   - This version include basic support for reading and writing DDS topics
   
   - No support is currently provided for QoS, this will be added next

   - No support for Listeners or Waitsets. Listeners will be added shortly
   and waitset before the general release.

   - The current version of simd-cxx 1.0 has been verified to compile with 
   the following compiler:

      Apple clang version 3.1 (tags/Apple/clang-318.0.58) (based on LLVM 3.1svn)
      Target: x86_64-apple-darwin11.3.0
      Thread model: posix
